_sText:
This map is to train your awp skill.
There's a wooden target on each part.
There are 5 Parts.

Destroy the whole wooden part (head, body, both arms, both legs).
You can see green lights on the right side, if all turned on, then you destroyed the wooden target.
Go into the hole to go to the next part. The hole will open if you destroyed the wooden target.
On the left side theres a timer. You'll die if you need to long.

On the last Part (5th), if you destroyed the wooden target, a new target will come, which looks red, I think you'll see it. Just hit it once and a Text will come.


Only one player can play. The others will have no weapon.
ONLY TERRORISTS!
Max. 8 Players.


I guess there are some Bugs, please let me now.

It's the Alpha!


My english isn't the best - sry.
